  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0 \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Independent journalist Antony Veranga is detained",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today (28) Kadwala Magistrate Court has ordered that the former President of Ruhunu University Students' Union, former member of the editorial board of 'Anitha' magazine, independent media journalist Antony Veranga Pushpika be remanded until August 9.",
        "Police said that on June 10, Antony Veranga Pushpikava was arrested for protesting against the court order in front of the Ministry of Education located in Isurubaya, Bhattaramulla.",
        "In this situation, he has been remanded until the 9th of August as per the request of the police to make him undergo an identification parade.",
        "Yesterday (27) he participated in a demonstration by civil activists against the suppression of the government in front of the Fort railway station, then when he was boarding a bus to go home, 6 people entered the bus and forcibly dragged Antony Veranga Pushpika and took him in a jeep.",
        "A group including lawyer Nuvan Popage, who was among the protestors, witnessed the incident and informed the Sri Lankan Human Rights Commission in this regard.",
        "After the Sri Lankan Human Rights Commission intervened, the police informed the Human Rights Commission that they had arrested journalist Anthony Veranga.",
        "He was arrested by the Colombo South Criminal Investigation Department and detained at Pambalapitiya Police Station yesterday evening. It was learned that steps had been taken to hand him over to the Fort Police.",
        "The Fort police have investigated him in connection with the demonstration held in front of the police headquarters on June 10 and then handed him over to the Thalangama police. Talangama Police has produced him in the Kaduwale Court and he has been kept in remand."
      ],
